title: Hour 1 - MLB Playoffs, Commanders Have No Excuses
itunes:title: Hour 1 - MLB Playoffs, Commanders Have No Excuses
description:
Dan talks about the MLB Playoffs and whether it's more compelling than tonight's lackluster NFL matchup between the Washington Commanders and Chicago Bears. And he thinks the Commanders don't have an excuse for their terrible performance so far this season. .
